{"tid":1602651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"攻入水馬先有用","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:21:18.000Z","uid":40518,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b241c7ab9ab9b4be1ef6459856df3d348760e58","tid":1602651,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過每次都係水馬外面圍有咩用<br />\n每次都係喺出面硬食顏色水，TG, <br />\n之後等狗出黎突襲 拉哂我地啲手足！<br />\n點解唔係我地攻入先，再施火魔法呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地掟彈落地下係冇撚用架</span></span><br />\n我地應該要有繩拉冧啲水馬啊！<br />\n攻入先會令啲狗驚！打亂佢地計畫！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">930 大三罷<br />\n101 賀國慶</span></span>"},{"pid":"df0797f3f821f18d8336e9bd853e4705c94ac61b","tid":1602651,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"411d82c531588f428505fb02241186b7596c9840","tid":1602651,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2426da02292d3aa1765cfcc1ad876586ee33ac5b","tid":1602651,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b326ffef37900cc3014207d48be50c6646255e4","tid":1602651,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fcbc720f94c8ea91e8ae6d44d9b2029e6d3e69","tid":1602651,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"要有車先易拉"},{"pid":"f72df11067d5b2dacd4177b09c6fd27a18037807","tid":1602651,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"ae7f8efffab9d0d976c876dc191b5d38ef22da0b","tid":1602651,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"